These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: writing, woodworking
Job: journalist, fisherman
1. Job:journalist is in an even position##4
2. Job:fisherman == Hobby:woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | woodworking | writing |
| Job     | fisherman    | journalist   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: tea, water
Sport: handball, biathlon
1. Sport:handball is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:water is on the left of Beverage:tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | water | tea        |
| Sport      | handball  | biathlon |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: classical, reggae
Nationality: italian, french
1. Nationality:italian is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:reggae is on the left of Music-Genre:classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae    | classical |
| Nationality   | italian | french |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
Beverage: tea, hot-chocolate
Food: plum, cabbage
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the right of Beverage:tea##1
2. Food:cabbage is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | tea      | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | plum | cabbage    |

